reviewText:
This is one of my favorite movies.
It doesn't seem as if stories are written like these anymore!
This was Jaspal Bhatti's birthday request and he was very pleased...

I loved this movie. I remember watching as a teenager, and wanted to see it again. A story of love, opportunity,circumstances, self descipline,trust, mistrustm corruption..very gently intertwined. Excellent acting by rajesh khanna..one of his best movie..a must see for romance,story,performence,music...
